line="850" spacing="600" horzpos="0" horzsize="51024" flags="393216"/><hp:lineseg textpos="32" vertpos="33600" vertsize="1000" textheight="1000" baseline="850" spacing="600" horzpos="0" horzsize="51024" flags="393216"/></hp:linesegarray></hp:p><hp:p id="0" paraPrIDRef="0" styleIDRef="0" pageBreak="0" columnBreak="0" merged="0"><hp:run charPrIDRef="0"/><hp:linesegarray><hp:lineseg textpos="0" vertpos="35200" vertsize="1000" textheight="1000" baseline="850" spacing="600" horzpos="0" horzsize="51024" flags="393216"/></hp:linesegarray></hp:p><hp:p id="2147483648" paraPrIDRef="0" styleIDRef="0" pageBreak="0" columnBreak="0" merged="0"><hp:run charPrIDRef="0"><hp:t>2. 표준 개인정보처리방침 (전문)</hp:t></hp:run><hp:linesegarray><hp:lineseg textpos="0" vertpos="36800" vertsize="1000" textheight="1000" baseline="850" spacing="600" horzpos="0" horzsize="51024" flags="393216"/></hp:linesegarray></hp:p><hp:p id="2147483648" paraPrIDRef="0" styleIDRef="0" pageBreak="0" columnBreak="0" merged="0"><hp:run charPrIDRef="0"/><hp:linesegarray><hp:lineseg textpos="0" vertpos="38400" vertsize="1000" textheight="1000" baseline="850" spacing="600" horzpos="0" horzsize="51024" flags="393216"/></hp:linesegarray></hp:p><hp:p id="0" paraPrIDRef="0" styleIDRef="0" pageBreak="0" columnBreak="0" merged="0"><hp:run charPrIDRef="0"><hp:t>  [ingyu’s ai world](이하 본 서비스)은(는) 개인정보 보호법 제30조에 따라 정보주체의 개인정보를 보호하고 이와 관련한 고충을 신속하고 원활하게 처리할 수 있도록 하기 위하여 다음과 같이 개인정보 처리방침을 수립·공개합니다.</hp:t></hp:run><hp:linesegarray><hp:lineseg textpos="0" vertpos="40000" vertsize="1000" textheight="1000" baseline="850" spacing="600" horzpos="0" horzsize="51024" flags="393216"/><hp:lineseg textpos="70" vertpos="41600" vertsize="1000" textheight="1000" baseline="850" spacing="600" horzpos="0" horzsize="51024" flags="393216"/><hp:lineseg textpos="129" vertpos="43200" vertsize="1000" textheight="1000" baseline="850" spacing="600" horzpos="0" horzsize="51024" flags="393216"/></hp:linesegarray></hp:p><hp:p id="2147483648" paraPrIDRef="0" style